{"tid":1797061,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯GG了 比祖雲達斯搶走haaland     含大師級分析! (恥笑emoji)","createTime":"2019-12-25T06:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T05:27:12.000Z","uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"61399b3ed2ab2b539663e70126cc09478fb981f4","tid":1797061,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"haaland係比Kane更可怕的Kane 2世!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1787204/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1787204/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n西瓜老啦 踢得果 1、2年 佢仲要唔肯減薪<br />\n仲要係字改稅率前簽 仲要係第2高薪(唔計免簽果D) 7.5M<br />\nM子走左 kean子走左<br />\n中鋒wo? 咪得西瓜一個<br />\n戴巴拿唔係 C朗可以係 但唔肯做 霸死左翼位<br />\nC朗肯做中鋒戰術係可以多圓化D 可惜次次出親都有西瓜同戴巴陪打正前<br />\n西瓜30幾歲 M子又唔肯做後備開季前已經玩野同高層搞彎左<br />\n<br />\n唯一係點? 唯一咪收番kean 但你唔好忘記<br />\n佢都係拉奧拿做經理人 咪一鳩樣?<br />\n加上佢係愛記表現比唔到信心 仲搞到愛記就黎降班<br />\n愛記係有重用過佢 但真係交唔出表現 即係即食唔到啦<br />\n屌你之前賣比人都27.5M英鎊 咪又係30M歐?<br />\n愛記會唔會蝕賣呀?<br />\n就咁睇 買haaland係一個好好既選擇<br />\n<br />\n總結買haaland原因:<br />\n1. M子走左 kean子走左 得西瓜一個老中鋒介要唔知踢到1定2年兼人工貴<br />\n2. C朗唔肯做中鋒 2翼選擇少一個 速度慢哂落黎 西瓜又係慢<br />\n3. 收番kean子係唯一選擇 但打唔起 即食唔到之餘後備換佢都無信心<br />\n4. haaland補1、2點問題 速度快左好多 白人合作性有望幫到沙里<br />\n5. 同 kean子一樣年輕 差幾個月 潛力股打唔起但踢過大球會加經理係拉奧拿一定賣得出<br />\n6. 祖記唔怕佢走佬 有錢賺就夠 加上走佬唔係1-2年後既事 又要迫住係c朗仲打得既1-2年下要博 所以點都係好事<br />\nps: 完美分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簽過廢過西瓜既不如唔好簽 勁過西瓜又咁有後備有幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只有潛力強大既幼幼可簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6mPHzpXtzA&amp;t=69s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DK6mPHzpXtzA%26t%3D69s&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=2ec8ae7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K6mPHzpXtzA&amp;t=69s</a>"},{"pid":"0a1d8bfdf32ee917eefdf7c3eab2c6ec85980304","tid":1797061,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"一邊就拎冠踢歐戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另一邊就。。。。。"},{"pid":"5c9fd7920a3120c06c61f92cddd513f0e71266c3","tid":1797061,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"曼聯需要傳送好既防中 唔係需要前鋒<br />\n曼聯買唔到先好"},{"pid":"87adfaa2475f940d392728645d38cbb561ce2f73","tid":1797061,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a1d8bfdf32ee917eefdf7c3eab2c6ec85980304","tid":1797061,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"一邊就拎冠踢歐戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />另一邊就。。。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"32d00e3e03696703c97b2bf1b08cb68374d5853d","tid":1797061,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35d1d6d3e0d9d963d85cb7bcdd696a9024f7aeed","tid":1797061,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:09:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0834a38c2464e1f2b9422ab140731a3c40c5a8d","tid":1797061,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:29:35.000Z","msg":"自己推自己post 打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6158d4121521ff537b3712b13cf886f58465a9","tid":1797061,"uid":293539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c9fd7920a3120c06c61f92cddd513f0e71266c3","tid":1797061,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"